<lb n="0577a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0577a1401">爾時大遍照金剛如來。說此妙歌讚已。復說
<lb n="0577a15" ed="T"/>供養真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0577a16" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0577a1601">唵<note place="inline">引</note>阿<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0577006" n="0577006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0577006" n="0577006"/>耨<anchor xml:id="end0577006"/>怛囉<note place="inline">一</note>薩哩嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>布<note place="inline">引</note>惹<note place="inline">引</note>彌<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0577007" n="0577007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0577007" n="0577007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0577007" n="0577007"/><note place="inline">引</note><anchor xml:id="end0577007"/>
